Class EventData

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.ac.ariel.liortamir.javalab.bl.EventData

  • public class EventData
extends java.lang.Object
    A container class holding the data of a request or its response.
    The class contains getters and setters for int, double, String and LocalDateTime.
    The key for each field must come from API
    Author:
    liort
